(1, 'alt', 'seo title', 'alt2', 'title2', 'alt3', 'title3', 'alt4', 'title4', '                <h1 xss=removed>SLICK PATTERN STORY</h1>                                         \r\n                                            \r\n                                            \r\n                                            \r\n   ', '                <span xss=removed>India’s largest omnichannel beauty destination</span>                                         \r\n                                            \r\n                                            \r\n                                 ', '                <p class=\"text-center text-justify\" xss=removed>Since our launch, we have not only redefined the art of e-retailing beauty and personal care in India, but also have been instrumental in fostering the growth of a previously relatively nasce', '1705313881aboutus_1.jpg', '                                                <h2 class=\"p-0 pageheading \" xss=removed>SLICKPATTERN FEATURES IN THE PRESTIGIOUS ANNUAL TIME100</h2>                                         \r\n                                           \r\n                  ', '                                                <h2 class=\"p-0 pageheading \" xss=removed>MOST INFLUENTIAL COMPANIES LIST 2022</h2>                                         \r\n                                           \r\n                                     ', '                                                <span xss=removed>Ten years after being founded by entrepreneur Falguni Nayar with the goal of inspiring Indian women, SlickPattern has evolved into one of India’s largest cosmetics and lifestyle brands.</span><br>                                         \r\n                                           \r\n                                           \r\n                                           \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>OUR MISSION</h2>                             \r\n                               \r\n                               \r\n                               \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>OUR VISION</h2>                              \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n  ', '            <span xss=removed>To create a world where our consumers have access to a finely curated, authentic assortment of products and services that delight and elevate the human spirit.</span>                          \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n  ', '            <span xss=removed>Bring inspiration and joy to people, everywhere, everyday.</span>                       \r\n                         \r\n                         \r\n                         \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>OUR VALUES</h2>                        \r\n                          \r\n                          \r\n                          \r\n  ', 'press_2_1705319483.avif', '            <h2 xss=removed>A DAY IN THE LIFE OF SLICKPATTERN</h2>                         \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n  ', 'press_3_1705319483.avif', ' \r\n   We’ve tried to transform the way India shops for beauty and that hasn’t been easy. Luckily for us, we have an incredible team that loves a challenge. Our team is constantly growing and evolving and we’re always on the look-out for young, energetic, highly-motivated superheroes to come aboard. \r\n          \r\n       \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>OUR LEADERSHIP TEAM</h2>                             \r\n                               \r\n                               \r\n                               \r\n  ', 'press_4_1705319483.avif', '            <h2 xss=removed>ARE YOU KEEN TO JOIN OUR TEAM?</h2>                         \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n  ', '         We have developed systems and processes to ensure that the products sold on our platform are authentic, and build trust among our consumers and brands. For our beauty and personal care offering, our business is predominantly inventory led. This approach ensures sourcing directly from brands or their authorized distributors in India. It allows us to guarantee authenticity of products bought by our consumers, an important consideration for consumers of such products. We also conduct quality checks at our warehouses periodically on our beauty and personal care products. For our fashion offering, we operate a managed marketplace and ensure that the sellers we onboard are authorized resellers only. We have also developed systems to monitor and address consumer complaints towards our ongoing commitment to authenticity.                          \r\n      ', '            <span xss=removed>If you feel you’ve got what it takes, get in touch at careers@nykaa.com</span>                         \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>AUTHENTICITY</h2>                         \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n  ', '      <span xss=removed>We have developed systems and processes to ensure that the products sold on our platform are authentic, and build trust among our consumers and brands. For our beauty and personal care offering, our business is predominantly inventory led. This approach ensures sourcing directly from brands or their authorized distributors in India. It allows us to guarantee authenticity of products bought by our consumers, an important consideration for consumers of such products. We also conduct quality checks at our warehouses periodically on our beauty and personal care products. For our fashion offering, we operate a managed marketplace and ensure that the sellers we onboard are authorized resellers only. We have also developed systems to monitor and address consumer complaints towards our ongoing commitment to authenticity.</span>    ', '            <h2 xss=removed>PRESS</h2>                         \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n                           \r\n  ', '            <h2 xss=removed>NEW LAUNCHES</h2>                       \r\n                         \r\n                         \r\n                         \r\n  ', 'true', '2024-03-21 01:42:01 PM');

