 for stain removing.</li><li xss=\"removed\">A list of care instructions/symbols are provided by the designer and if any of those instructions are also not followed properly.</li></ul><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2337/7003/files/Laundry_Care_Symbols-01-1024x683.jpg?v=1624091522\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2337/7003/files/Laundry_Care_Symbols-01-1024x683.jpg?v=1624091522\" class=\"img-fluid w-100 lazy\" xss=\"removed\"></div></h2></center></div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            ', '                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             